de: Addendum No 2 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and the Republic of Poland represented by the Ministry of Regional Development as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project KIK/39 "Pilot asbestos waste Management System reinforced with working quantity monitoring and control system of the waste removal and neutralisation in Lubelskie Voivodeship"  - 28-04-2015 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Polen, vertreten durch das Ministerium für regionale Entwicklung, bezüglich der Überwachung und Entsorgung von Asbest, Projekt KIK/39
